item.title: First Post
item.description:
SelfIntroduce

Hi, I’m Hung-Chi, originally from Taiwan. I recently moved to Toronto and have over three years of experience as a back-end developer, primarily working with Java. My expertise is in API development, and I’m excited about the opportunity to contribute my skills to a new team here in Canada.
